{"tid":131931,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚做緊/做過酒店嘅巴絲, 有冇想/已經轉工轉行嘅可以入黎分享下","createTime":"2017-02-23T12:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T08:21:41.000Z","uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c2924b13ccee156b66442f1df8c004e6d2ce2e48","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"本身唔係讀hospitality<br />\n嗰時同老媽子頂頸唔想日日放工番去同佢面左左就諗住搵份通宵工做<br />\n初頭想去上個保安人員許可證之後做保安(個title 係in通宵客戶服務員實際係食蕉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來有fd咁介紹我黎呢做front desk<br />\n<br />\n而家番左長通一年半開始有啲想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n猶豫嘅原因係公司啲同事好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> dept老細同同事都幾好人相處唔錯<br />\n因為聽過另外做酒店啲fd講佢地班同事完全唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n據講佢地自己dept本身都有埋堆有小圈子<br />\nA dept head 唔妥 B dept head<br />\n幾個dept成日互對大家<br />\n再諗到自己公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上我地dept而家已經唔夠人(之前走左個<br />\n如果我都開口嗌走就得番4丁友<br />\n好仆街咁樣<br />\n<br />\n同埋想走又唔知之後搵咩工好<br />\n因為唔太想做番酒店<br />\n一諗到自己呢度算少房都日日有濕9閪客麻煩嘢就唔想轉其他大啲嘅酒店試下<br />\n加上聽埋好多人唱衰今年市道驚自己出去揾唔番or俾人cut<br />\n<br />\n但係份工真係低人工左啲同離我屋企遠<br />\n另外就係很肯定我係冇得升<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好十五十六<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做緊酒店又心大心細走定唔走嘅巴絲可唔以分享下你地咩情形<br />\n<br />\n又或者做過酒店已經甩左身嘅可唔可以分享下or俾啲意見黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55d6de9a70aafe985445dd5467f2304c4db5fdb","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f0285bb12c6c09c6685347e5a8763c430060c7","tid":131931,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"細酒店FO通宵更得1,2個，頂多加個DM同bell仔<br />\n同事好唔好關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n走啦，人工又底，身體又差，斷六親，同社會脫晒節"},{"pid":"c986c684ae13399ca8da98571e6cff9a4491c03e","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細酒店FO通宵更得1,2個，頂多加個DM同bell仔<br />\n同事好唔好關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n走啦，人工又底，身體又差，斷六親，同社會脫晒節</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇Bell <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過幾次三更半夜行出去幫人搬行李<br />\n最怕係中東佬, 佢地個個都當正旅行好似搬屋咁<br />\n最誇張嗰次2公婆帶住個2,3歲嘅細路但有5個大喼(重到我搬唔郁)2個中喼仲有bb車<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實出面酒店fo幾錢一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔熟行情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嗰時懵下懵下咁佢又好等人用就咁就入左黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2339872dd43dea53905659429871d41646576a87","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:21:03.000Z","msg":"隔日推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7dda46b058c79d3e2976291fd1436bed21a1e55","tid":131931,"uid":18143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T20:26:48.000Z","msg":"做fo真係壓力好大，做細酒店就要做埋concierge bell果d，做大酒店跟standard仲有勁多paperwork同goal，工時又長到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申做左3個月大牌酒店頂唔順quit左依家搵緊其他工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cb27ef1f1c0e5ba9d7abd1c0c128c85e6be6a4","tid":131931,"uid":21844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T20:36:47.000Z","msg":"我果間FO 人工兩雞未計upsell 通宵都係一個+FOAM 不過有400間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b0e54021e3e212245bae736143de1adc60a40b","tid":131931,"uid":14940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T21:35:21.000Z","msg":"做緊細酒店fo 儲緊1年工作經驗想去working holiday 但其實唔想入酒店呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28c32022969581f524173376d093fa51e523f2e","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果間FO 人工兩雞未計upsell 通宵都係一個+FOAM 不過有400間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絲打番邊區未計upsell已經咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係細酒店都真係below average<br />\n今年加完先挨近13k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7241d7d4192954010d31a3f5520c910c813d3ac","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做fo真係壓力好大，做細酒店就要做埋concierge bell果d，做大酒店跟standard仲有勁多paperwork同goal，工時又長到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申做左3個月大牌酒店頂唔順quit左依家搵緊其他工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做緊細酒店fo 儲緊1年工作經驗想去working holiday 但其實唔想入酒店呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做細酒店冇咁多standard跟但就一腳踢<br />\nRes, Concierge, 忙起上黎RA做唔切房fo都要幫手<br />\n夜晚RA Engine 放左工又係<br />\n啲客要咩/間房有咩事都要自己硬食晒<br />\n<br />\n做大brand又係慘, 如果FO齊team都叫好啲, 唔齊嘅話忙起上黎做到係想走都冇得走爆OT做到hi hi咁<br />\n最慘係越升得高越多OT<br />\nFOM長期番7收8"},{"pid":"436226921ca3114638e312de9b942933a97b5c04","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"有冇轉左行嘅巴絲出黎講下之後轉左咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49db17be8d1f5af172d5277dcb13a1e99cc20c47","tid":131931,"uid":21844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我果間FO 人工兩雞未計upsell 通宵都係一個+FOAM 不過有400間房<img src=\"/as