/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35dd67adda80bb6bddbc754125e261af5ca0804c","tid":131931,"uid":64525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T04:34:39.000Z","msg":"做緊細檔差唔多兩年 小錢冇得升 想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd160d930bca5682501426ccc5c003f31968283","tid":131931,"uid":21844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果間FO 人工兩雞未計upsell 通宵都係一個+FOAM 不過有400間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絲打番邊區未計upsell已經咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係細酒店都真係below average<br />\n今年加完先挨近13k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>港島區大檔 我做back office人工少1k 不過唔駛對客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊間人工咁高?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早排報紙新聞日日提到果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea5ecd58c9ca87e03f8287878c67d6912c5a124","tid":131931,"uid":76826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:01:52.000Z","msg":"平均每星期返幾多日？<br />\n年假有幾日？<br />\n易唔易加升職加薪？<br />\n<br />\n非酒店科Fresh Grad，啱啱收到Front Desk offer, 接近萬四起薪。唔知自己係咪真係想喺呢行發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8eaa1fa862c889906731438e31e8fd7c10218ba","tid":131931,"uid":18143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平均每星期返幾多日？<br />\n年假有幾日？<br />\n易唔易加升職加薪？<br />\n<br />\n非酒店科Fresh Grad，啱啱收到Front Desk offer, 接近萬四起薪。唔知自己係咪真係想喺呢行發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做下先囉，多數2星期放3日，頭一個月都應該有排你學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cfbc4f64a5ef8cbc63c7e331b01e611210785f","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊間人工咁高?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早排報紙新聞日日提到果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講日日新聞有提我爭啲以為係沙田間regal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過港島區應該係four sss?"},{"pid":"2b33f1cb24d15505bc9ddacb5b562b25b6d70ac0","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平均每星期返幾多日？<br />\n年假有幾日？<br />\n易唔易加升職加薪？<br />\n<br />\n非酒店科Fresh Grad，啱啱收到Front Desk offer, 接近萬四起薪。唔知自己係咪真係想喺呢行發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做下先囉，多數2星期放3日，頭一個月都應該有排你學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一個月大把嘢學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣我都係未做過走入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然做酒店嘅好多都屌番呢行而家唔好做<br />\n但係起碼做fo人工有番咁上下又唔洗點孭數先<del>因為上面捽都唔係捽你</del>"},{"pid":"abe4c632d0a732ec6aa4aae0dcbb898f197b711a","tid":131931,"uid":16546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:12:15.000Z","msg":"有冇bell仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c2622c8e7d570baf40cd1073e3cc6cbdcb50fd","tid":131931,"uid":31108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:49:14.000Z","msg":"Hskp<br />\n個人比較靜 好似都唔係幾啱依行..."},{"pid":"fa25a1b88c0c654c7f5f5faee566605c0e03be50","tid":131931,"uid":367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"岩岩入行 好彩人工算高 人事又好<br />\n做得唔開心就唔好繼續做喇！"},{"pid":"ab21c054f82742299539baa441e932c0a88389c8","tid":131931,"uid":367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T15:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊間人工咁高?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早排報紙新聞日日提到果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講日日新聞有提我爭啲以為係沙田間regal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過港島區應該係four sss?</blockquote><br />\n應該4季啦 未計apartment岩岩好400房"},{"pid":"f8f98a072fe31936616b514c6659e7a3b2338179","tid":131931,"uid":26707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"有無人講下訂房部有咩做嫁？ 難唔難上手？"},{"pid":"5a658d43d12d05b4060bd904424d7a9369008ea3","tid":131931,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果間FO 人工兩雞未計upsell 通宵都係一個+FOAM 不過有400間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n絲打番邊區未計upsell已經咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係細酒店都真係below average<br />\n今年加完先挨近13k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>港島區大檔 我做back office人工少1k 不過唔駛對客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有酒店褔利，花紅又唔洗對客<br />\n入到back office =上左岸<br />\n識親讀酒店d女都想做hr"},{"pid":"b95556044a1a86af81500b3edb1ea086811a1b08","tid":131931,"uid":55193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"我識果班讀酒店出身而且比較醒目既都轉晒去做保險 呢一行呢一科真係投入同回報最唔成正比"},{"pid":"f25b5b3947bbcf18cef78f3f22cd157b0e9082bd","tid":131931,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"簡單講下喇<br />\n以穩定同福利黎講酒店其實真係唔差<br />\n最主要係睇你地做咩department <br />\n如果因為低人工而想轉行 不如搵多幾間睇下先再決定<br />\n如果因為要返night而想轉行 咁就冇得講 除非你做到office果班或者經理級 收5點<br />\n有巴打問冇任何酒店經驗同學歷做唔做到酒店<br />\n係做到既 酒店炒散暫時都係好缺"},{"pid":"06497a0aa5e4d82053dbe0f72ca084e702dcebd9","tid":131931,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人講下訂房部有咩做嫁？ 難唔難上手？</blockquote><br />\n訂房部其實就係你入酒店見到幫人check in check out果班 一開始唔洗對客 對旅行社only 幫佢地搞訂房果堆 上左手就要對客 有客打落黎要求咩 你就要記低 叫其他部門同事 e.g 個客要毛巾 你聽完就叫其他部門拎上去 以我認知係咁"},{"pid":"991de963caa1da2f806adbba77a31d33f6166939","tid":131931,"uid":31108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人講下訂房部有咩做嫁？ 難唔難上手？</blockquote><br />\n訂房部其實就係你入酒店見到幫人check in check out果班 一開始唔洗對客 對旅行社only 幫佢地搞訂房果堆 上左手就要對客 有客打落黎要求咩 你就要記低 叫其他部門同事 e.g 個客要毛巾 你聽完就叫其他部門拎上去 以我認知係咁</blockquote><br />\n訂房應該=/=Fo？"},{"pid":"e118c366b6473f927f1597fb978c8e85ec5c18cc","tid":131931,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無人講下訂房部有咩做嫁？ 難唔難上手？</blockquote><br />\n訂房部其實就係你入酒店見到幫人check in check out果班 一開始唔洗對客 對旅行社only 幫佢地搞訂房果堆 上左手就要對客 有客打落黎要求咩 你就要記低 叫其他部門同事 e.g 個客要毛巾 你聽完就叫其他部門拎上去 以我認知係咁</blockquote><br />\n訂房應該=/=Fo？</blockquote><br />\n訂房係要做埋Front desk agent"},{"pid":"cb00cd3ed13a3b6e614158db81483fa14d8981f1","tid":131931,"uid":31108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無人講下訂房部有咩做嫁？ 難唔難上手？</blockquote><br />\n訂房部其實就係你入酒店見到幫人check in check out果班 一開始唔洗對客 對旅行社only 幫佢地搞訂房果堆 上左手就要對客 有客打落黎要求咩 你就要記低 叫其他部門同事 e.g 個客要毛巾 你聽完就叫其他部門拎上去 以我認知係咁</blockquote><br />\n訂房應該=/=Fo？</blockquote><br />\n訂房係要做埋Front desk agent</blockquote><br />\n咁可能間間唔同<br />\n我個間訂房長坐office"},{"pid":"4440d4f9b4916ca02d5c2ce8f3badcc980fdc33d","tid":131931,"uid":43899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T09:32:18.000Z","msg":"酒店係咪年年有花紅分，大約點樣計算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05d42fedb1d3f71300c1fb03b8db00ceb04ebf