><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nF&amp;B最易無大糧或者最小<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟岩岩由酒店F&amp;B轉左地盤</blockquote><br />\n普遍餐廳真係唔賺錢<br />\n係宴會先賺到<br />\nCatering sales team 跟s&amp;m<br />\n個bonus就係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每間酒店都有KPI(積效指標)個名類似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d酒店係加分制有d就扣分既<br />\n<br />\n但好唔公平既係F&amp;B要跑數<br />\n但有d部門做好paperwork就有分<br />\n<br />\n點鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3797905fdf5f3fbaa3eac6db50f77bda3e36b9","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我識果班讀酒店出身而且比較醒目既都轉晒去做保險 呢一行呢一科真係投入同回報最唔成正比</blockquote><br />\n我都有聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我就係讀finance 出身唔想做保險跑數先黎做酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2980f07bee107b9e40391535939d2e03a5187c","tid":131931,"uid":86826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡單講下喇<br />\n以穩定同福利黎講酒店其實真係唔差<br />\n最主要係睇你地做咩department <br />\n如果因為低人工而想轉行 不如搵多幾間睇下先再決定<br />\n如果因為要返<span style=\"color: red;\">night</span>而想轉行 咁就冇得講 除非你做到office果班或者<span style=\"color: blue;\">經理級 收5點</span><br />\n有巴打問冇任何酒店經驗同學歷做唔做到酒店<br />\n係做到既 酒店炒散暫時都係好缺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n番<span style=\"color: red;\">overnight</span>其實我係ok嘅, 讀書嗰陣慣晒。趕project做日出黨就唔洗講啦, 但平時冇嘢做淨係追下新番/等下字幕都差唔多3,4點先瞓<br />\nconcern最多都係人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">但事實係升得越高OT越多</span><br />\nfo mgr 話就話係office hour, 照計係準時5點放, 實際上好多時都搞下搞下做到7,8點先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但朝朝早6點幾就番到公司<br />\n放完大假一落機冇耐就番公司做嘢<br />\nfo唔夠人要放低啲嘢出去頂fo 負責i/o<br />\nOT 啲鐘永遠清唔晒<br />\n以上係令我我想轉行嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5997743db350fac30918043428066ff39967062","tid":131931,"uid":367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我識果班讀酒店出身而且比較醒目既都轉晒去做保險 呢一行呢一科真係投入同回報最唔成正比</blockquote><br />\n我都有聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我就係讀finance 出身唔想做保險跑數先黎做酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係讀finance 但走左黎做酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地話ot好勁 香港有邊份工唔ot得勁架屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有 想入back office個班 有排都冇得升wo<br />\nOperation turnover 高 肯留低就排隊升<br />\n有學歷既仲吃香 operation同事多數都冇degree架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506785fb7d6988b2e4bf28384562b3c92acddcd3","tid":131931,"uid":57282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T22:13:57.000Z","msg":"唔好做狗富 完"},{"pid":"531712014f533b9c60054e694d77e977893ab0ca","tid":131931,"uid":24877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T22:21:23.000Z","msg":"無做過酒店 ， 只係我認為你覺得起馬呢份工你番得開心咪番住先 先年半 可能過多半年你就捨得走呢"},{"pid":"bfe1fe669b13eb3fccab0aef50dacc672a4e189e","tid":131931,"uid":8218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T22:25:51.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ead4febfad0e591318f79f2d7e88251b61aa5225","tid":131931,"uid":2397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T22:37:05.000Z","msg":"讀緊hospitality 遲下要做placement 有冇邊間好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bc9ec67dd39c4071f1e046baeed0784c03543c","tid":131931,"uid":2603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T22:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀緊hospitality 遲下要做placement 有冇邊間好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大檔 intern  hea到仆街 返去唔係睇波就睇下馬 埋到堆 真係四平八穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor