客？係味多數用email同客聯繫？"},{"pid":"bd7a749ba0ce23f391daa304668e176aee2b2db2","tid":131931,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀緊hospitality 遲下要做placement 有冇邊間好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大檔 intern  hea到仆街 返去唔係睇波就睇下馬 埋到堆 真係四平八穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大檔即係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5星級，大集團，類似呢d掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5b883b5aa3ca3235cbbb3ac7a819ca7486af20","tid":131931,"uid":21313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:31:44.000Z","msg":"Bell仔轉去front desk留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nConcierge雖然冇乜前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但個陣真係開心好多"},{"pid":"dac4787cc686fbb301583a1fd64b160bfe84b464","tid":131931,"uid":18143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T20:52:47.000Z","msg":"最慘既莫過於你讀唔讀hospitality根本唔重要，一切都經驗為先，promotion你有個19 degree都夠啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw 做過fo你成間酒店應該咩位都冇問題"},{"pid":"5c64efa4260bace7cb6413b1641354d4db6d8d18","tid":131931,"uid":2397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T23:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀緊hospitality 遲下要做placement 有冇邊間好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大檔 intern  hea到仆街 返去唔係睇波就睇下馬 埋到堆 真係四平八穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大檔即係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5星級，大集團，類似呢d掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港間間五星一樣？好驚簡左間d supervisor 係仆街 迫我做到隻狗咁 但又評到我勁低分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji